name: p3x-redis-ui
description: 📡 P3X Redis UI that uses Socket.IO, AngularJs Material and IORedis with statistics, console - terminal, tree, dark mode, internationalization, multiple connections, web and desktop by Electron. Works as an app without Node.JS GUI or with the latest Node.Js version. Can test it at https://p3x.redis.patrikx3.com/.
